Pralatrexate was approved by the FDA on September 24, 2009.[L37674] It is also being studied for other types of lymphoma and solid malignancy such as non-small-cell lung cancer, breast cancer, and bladder cancer.[A246678]', '["L01BA05"]', '[]');
